<figureCitation id="98F21AC48F44FECA48905178FEABF99C" box="[160,270,1620,1644]" captionStart="PLATE 77" captionStartId="268.[151,232,1917,1940]" captionTargetBox="[244,1398,221,1861]" captionTargetId="figure-96@268.[151,1436,193,1896]" captionText="PLATE 77. A, B, F, G. Chelae, holotypes. C. Pronotum, lateral view. D, E. Heads, holotypes. A. Dryinus choui (from Olmi 1993b). B. D. exilis (from Olmi 1984). C. D. expolitus, female from Ryukyu (from Mita, 2009b). D, G. D. fulvus (from Olmi 1984). E. D. hainanensis (from Olmi 1987a). F. D. expolitus (from Xu et al. 2007). Scale bar 0.27 mm for A, 0.29 mm for B, 0.35 mm for F and G" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6413001" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6413001/files/figure.png" pageId="266" pageNumber="267">Plate 77B</figureCitation>
